Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:31.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,东西都带全了吗\N{\rENG}So you got everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:33.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,你打算在飞机上一直玩游戏\N{\rENG}You gonna play video games all flight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.87,0:00:35.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,还是打算真的看会书\N{\rENG}or do you think you might actually crack open a book?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.63,0:00:37.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,大概会看会书\N{\rENG}Probably read some.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:41.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,别害怕给我回邮件 好吗\N{\rENG}If I write you an e-mail, don't be scared to write me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:43.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,让老爸了解下你的想法和近况\N{\rENG}Ok? It won't kill you to let your old man know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:45.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,又不会要了你的命\N{\rENG}what you're thinking about or what is going on, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:46.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:47.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,你愿意的话\N{\rENG}If you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:49.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,咱们每周可以用网络电话聊聊天\N{\rENG}we can try Skyping once a week or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:50.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rENG}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:54.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,自然科学课画的那些图纸带了吗\N{\rENG}You got the drawings for your science deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:56.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 应该带了  - 好吧\N{\rENG}- Yeah. I think so.  - Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:58.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,你做得很好 真的特别棒\N{\rENG}Well, they turned out great by the way, like really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:00:59.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rENG}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:02.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你的电脑充好电了吗  - 充好了\N{\rENG}- Is your computer charged?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:08.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,等你到家以后\N{\rENG}What do you think is the first thing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:09.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,你第一件要做的事是什么\N{\rENG}you are going to do when you get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:12.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\rENG}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:15.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,我很珍惜咱们这次交流的机会\N{\rENG}I really cherish this communication we have, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.79,0:01:19.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 只是你的回答都有点…  - 怎么了\N{\rENG}- It's just... your answers are so...  - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:22.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,坚持练习弹钢琴 好吗\N{\rENG}Just keep practicing the piano, Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:22.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,你弹得很棒\N{\rENG}You're really good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.94,0:01:24.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且你都费了那么大功夫了\N{\rENG}and they spend so much time at that school of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:26.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,别忘了音乐这东西\N{\rENG}Just... just remember that music is actually something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:28.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,会有助于你的生活\N{\rENG}that you'll use in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.24,0:01:30.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,别忘了…你要芝麻味的 对吧\N{\rENG}Don't forget to... you want those sesame things right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:31.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,那种特好吃\N{\rENG}They're really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:32.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:33.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rENG}Γεια σου!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:37.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:41.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,我大概十月能过去\N{\rENG}I probably make it over there in October.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:42.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,我会尽量赶去看你的第一次独奏\N{\rENG}I'll try to see you in that first recital
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:44.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,最好还能赶上看你踢场球赛\N{\rENG}and hopefully catch a soccer game while I'm there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:49.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rENG}Ευχαριστώ!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:51.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,今年我可能不会再踢足球了\N{\rENG}I might not even play soccer this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:54.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,这绝对是个错误的决定 相信我\N{\rENG}That would be a big mistake, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:56.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,我踢得不好\N{\rENG}I'm not that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:01:58.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 你踢得很好 非常好\N{\rENG}Oh no, you're pretty good, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.17,0:02:01.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,可是…我错过了夏季训练营\N{\rENG}I mean... I missed summer training camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:04.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以不太可能让我回去了\N{\rENG}so the chances of me starting are miniscule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:06.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,你直接告诉教练你的情况\N{\rENG}Yes, well, just tell the coach your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:09.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,你爸爸住在欧洲 你其实特想去\N{\rENG}Your dad lives in Europe and you really wanted to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:10.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是之类的借口 把责任推给我\N{\rENG}You know... blah, blah, blame me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:12.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,我父母太讨厌了 但是我很上心的\N{\rENG}my parents stink but I'm really serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:14.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是我没那么上心 爸爸\N{\rENG}But I'm not serious, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:16.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不是很在意那个\N{\rENG}I don't care that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:22.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,你也不用现在就做决定 多考虑考虑\N{\rENG}Well, you don't have to decide right now, just think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:24.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,我就是觉得团队运动很重要\N{\rENG}All I'm saying is that team sports are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:29.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,就到这儿了\N{\rENG}Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:33.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这个机场 你呢\N{\rENG}I love this airport, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:34.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,这里太酷了\N{\rENG}It's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:35.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,是吧 我也觉得很酷\N{\rENG}Yeah, I know it's cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:36.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,要见到你妈妈了 兴奋吗\N{\rENG}Are you excited about seeing your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:38.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 是啊 还有我的伙伴们  - 没错\N{\rENG}- Yeah, and all my friends.  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:40.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的登机牌和护照都带了吗\N{\rENG}What about your boarding pass, passport?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:43.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 转机你没问题吧\N{\rENG}Ok... Do you feel confident about making the connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:45.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,没事 我以前都是这样的\N{\rENG}Yes, I have done this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:47.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,但这次有点复杂\N{\rENG}Yes, but this is a tricky connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:50.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,飞机着陆后 记着坐着别起来\N{\rENG}Just remember that when you land you stay in your seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:51.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,会有航空公司的人来接你\N{\rENG}somebody from the airline is going to come get you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:52.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,把你带去登机口\N{\rENG}and take you to the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:53.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,记住了吗\N{\rENG}Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:56.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 没问题的  - 好吧\N{\rENG}- It's not a problem.  - Ok, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:02:59.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,伙计\N{\rENG}Oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:04.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,看来真的得说再见了 是吧\N{\rENG}Well... it looks like maybe we should just do this thing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:08.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,过来 天啊\N{\rENG}Ok, come here! Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:11.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,我会尽量赶去看你独奏的 好吗\N{\rENG}I'll do my best to make that recital, Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:14.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,其实…我不介意的\N{\rENG}You know... I wouldn't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:17.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,为什么这么说\N{\rENG}What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不是故意要刻薄你\N{\rENG}Look, I'm not being mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:21.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,但如果你不来看我独奏的话我会更轻松\N{\rENG}but it would be easier if you didn't come to the recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:22.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么会呢\N{\rENG}How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:25.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你选别的周末来看我更好\N{\rENG}It would just be better if you visited on a nothing weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想看你弹琴\N{\rENG}I want to see you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是妈妈真的很讨厌你\N{\rENG}Look. It's because mom hates you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:31.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你在 她会特别紧张\N{\rENG}She would be really stressed if you were there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,弄得我也很有压力\N{\rENG}and then it would be tense for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你知道吗  - 谢谢\N{\rENG}- You know...  - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:40.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且咱们也没有时间一起玩\N{\rENG}We wouldn't have any time to hang out anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:42.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,别担心 会有办法的\N{\rENG}Do not worry about it, we'll figure that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:45.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不希望你担心这个 好吗\N{\rENG}I just don't want you to worry about it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:49.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道我有多想你 对吧\N{\rENG}I mean... You know how much I miss you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:55.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,你为什么觉得她还那么讨厌我\N{\rENG}Why do you think she still hates me so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:56.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rENG}I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:03:59.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,我觉得相比起来她更讨厌丹尼尔一些\N{\rENG}I think she hates Daniel more than she hates you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:00.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:03.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,别担心 我会想办法的\N{\rENG}Hey, don't worry about it, I'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:04.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,我该进去了\N{\rENG}We should just do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:07.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 还有什么我能帮忙的吗\N{\rENG}Yeah, but is there anything I can do to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rENG}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:11.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 但是你知道我爱你 对吗  - 当然\N{\rENG}- But you know that I love you, right?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:14.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,我当然知道 这是我过得最好的一个夏天\N{\rENG}Yeah, I know! This has been the best summer of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 真的吗  - 真的\N{\rENG}- Really?  - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:18.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也这么想 看吧\N{\rENG}For me too, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,我就说过希腊会是个特别棒的地方\N{\rENG}I told you, this whole Greece thing was going to be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:21.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,确实是\N{\rENG}And it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:24.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,我爱你 伙计\N{\rENG}Ok! I love you, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:25.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也爱你 爸爸\N{\rENG}I love you too, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:27.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,来 握个手\N{\rENG}Ok... shake my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:29.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\rENG}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:36.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 好的\N{\rENG}Oui, oui!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,他跟德国人有个合作项目\N{\rENG}Il a un projet avec les Allemands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,像往常一样\N{\rENG}Comme d'habitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:06:00.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fsp20\shad0\c&H296863&}卡拉玛塔机场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:04.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,听我说 会议气氛太压抑了\N{\rENG}écoutez, on est stressé en cette réunion...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 不 我是说下周\N{\rENG}Non, bah, non. La semaine prochaine j'ai dit oui.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:10.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\fs65\fsp10\fscx150\shad2\4a&H33&\pos(985,895)}爱在午夜降临前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:19.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 那太好了\N{\rENG}Ok, bon, très bien.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:22.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢 您也一样 再见\N{\rENG}Merci, oui, oui, vous aussi hein. Au revoir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:23.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,我被排除在外了\N{\rENG}Ah, j'suis débusquée.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:25.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了  - 他们投票反对\N{\rENG}- What's going on?  - They voted against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,反对什么 安装风力涡轮机吗\N{\rENG}What? The wind turbines?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,和这些人打了六个月的交道\N{\rENG}6 months dealing with these people,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:29.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,好不容易都同意了\N{\rENG}they were all for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,大家都认为这对地区有好处\N{\rENG}Everyone agreed it was great for the region.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,那出什么岔子了\N{\rENG}So what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:34.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,现在他们都觉得涡轮机\N{\rENG}Now they've decided that they don't like the way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:34.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,放在山上的样子不好看\N{\rENG}that it looks on that hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:35.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们说那样有碍观瞻\N{\rENG}It's "Ruining their view."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:36.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,这件事不是都定下来了吗\N{\rENG}I thought it was a done deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:39.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 当时都说定了\N{\rENG}It was! It practically was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:40.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,那他们怎么还能这么做\N{\rENG}Can they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,当然 他们就这么做了 这事儿完了\N{\rENG}Of course! They've done it, and it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:45.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\rENG}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:47.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,没事 我只是太沮丧了\N{\rENG}No, no, it's so frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,我忍不下去了\N{\rENG}I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:54.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要接海米尔那活了\N{\rENG}I'm gonna take that job with Hemir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:56.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,别 你不想为他们工作\N{\rENG}No, you do not wanna work for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 为什么  - 为政府工作吗\N{\rENG}- Why not?  - For the government?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,我觉得这届政府和以往不同\N{\rENG}I think this government is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:03.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们需要法律支持 这是唯一的办法\N{\rENG}We need laws and it's the only way anything is gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:03.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,总有别的法子的\N{\rENG}That's not the only way,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:05.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们已经做了很多不错的工作了\N{\rENG}you guys have been getting a lot of good work done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:07.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,我考虑过了 只有这办法行得通\N{\rENG}Well, I've been thinking about it, this is the way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 那你可别忘了\N{\rENG}Ok, well then let me remind you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,你和那人合不来\N{\rENG}that you do not like that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:12.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,以前你在他那工作的时候\N{\rENG}The whole time you worked for him before
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:12.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,你整天都在抱怨\N{\rENG}you complained about him constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,没错 他是个混蛋\N{\rENG}Yeah, yeah, yeah... He can be an asshole
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:14.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是他能帮我把事搞定\N{\rENG}but he gets things done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:15.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,从现在开始我就得这么想了\N{\rENG}That's how I'm gonna be from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 我要做个贱人\N{\rENG}- Ok.  - A real bitch, Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:20.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,每次我见他都觉得他是狼子野心\N{\rENG}Well, every time I look at that guy all I see is ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:22.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,对不起 我就是不信任他\N{\rENG}I mean, I'm sorry, I don't trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:25.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,他从非营利部门转入政府的唯一原因\N{\rENG}The only reason he's going from not for profit to government
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:26.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是想有人能拍他马屁\N{\rENG}is to have people kiss his ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:27.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不在乎他怎么样 好吗\N{\rENG}I don't care about him, Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 我就是觉得你会过得特痛苦\N{\rENG}Ok, I think you are gonna be miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:33.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,面对数不清的政治活动和协商会议\N{\rENG}With all the politicking and compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:33.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,无所谓\N{\rENG}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:35.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,我已经决定了\N{\rENG}I've made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:37.68,ZHU,,0,0,0,,典出{\u1}古希腊神话{\u0}中诸神对西西弗斯的惩罚，让他每每接近成功又前功尽弃\N{\rCHS}我不想再做把大石头推上山\N{\rENG}I'm tired of being the do-gooder who rolls a boulder up a hill
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,再看着它滚下来的老好人了\N{\rENG}and watches it roll down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:40.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,他以前不是经常\N{\rENG}Wasn't he the guy who used to throw his pens
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,扔笔砸他的助理吗\N{\rENG}at his assistants and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:44.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,我一年前就该接这份工作了\N{\rENG}Ok, I should have taken this job a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:46.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,我害怕是因为工作量太大\N{\rENG}And I was scared because of the amount of work
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是我觉得这是个绝好的机会\N{\rENG}but I think it's the best opportunity ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:51.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,工资也更高 我决定了\N{\rENG}And it's more money, and I'm doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:54.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 你确定吗\N{\rENG}Ok, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:56.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,不确定 我什么都不确定 行吗\N{\rENG}No, I'm not sure of anything, Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:08:00.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我走了 那其他人都怎么办\N{\rENG}I mean, what's gonna happen to everyone if I leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:02.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,弗朗索瓦他们都指着我呢\N{\rENG}Like Francois... I mean, they count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢\N{\rENG}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:05.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我该不该接那个工作\N{\rENG}Should I take it or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 不 我不发表意见\N{\rENG}Oh, no no no, I don't have an opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:09.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我只是不想你因为风力涡轮机的失败\N{\rENG}No, I just don't want to see you rush into a decision
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:11.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,就匆忙做出决定\N{\rENG}because this wind turbine crap is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:13.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,不仅是因为那个 好吗\N{\rENG}It's not just that, Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:14.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,我都蠢蠢欲动一整个夏天了\N{\rENG}It's been stirring me all summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:16.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 不 我知道的  - 我要接这个工作 我决定了\N{\rENG}- No, I know it has, I know.  - I should do it. I'm doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:17.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,那就接吧\N{\rENG}Then do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:20.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,我决定了 好吗\N{\rENG}I'm doing it! Alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,上帝啊 我真希望事情都能简单些\N{\rENG}Oh God, I wish that things were simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:27.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,我走也完蛋 我留也完蛋\N{\rENG}I mean... if I leave I get fucked, if I stay I get fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:28.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,永远都不确定\N{\rENG}It's always a guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,没错 这就是个操蛋的世界\N{\rENG}Yeah, the world is fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:30.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,我觉得也是\N{\rENG}Yeah, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:33.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,天啊 好不容易能度个假期了\N{\rENG}Oh God, we finally have a vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,头两个星期姑娘们还生病了\N{\rENG}and the girls are sick for the first two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:36.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\rENG}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:38.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,有个完美儿子 却还住在一百万英里外\N{\rENG}With the perfect son who lives a million miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:41.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,或者是你毕生所爱\N{\rENG}Or the love of your life
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:43.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,刮完胡子不知道清理下\N{\rENG}who can't clean up after himself
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:44.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,还不肯学学怎么刮胡子\N{\rENG}or learn how to shave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.57,0:08:46.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,谁说的\N{\rENG}Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不是在说这的清洁队队长吧\N{\rENG}You're not talking about Captain Clean-up over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,清洁队队长\N{\rENG}Captain Clean-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:53.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,那个在行动中都失踪了好几年的人\N{\rENG}The one that's been missing in action all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,这时候你希望我说什么\N{\rENG}What did you expect at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:57.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\N{\rENG}God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧她们 太可爱了\N{\rENG}Oh look at them, they're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:04.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像连体婴儿似的\N{\rENG}They look like conjoined twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:06.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,天啊 我得给她们照张相\N{\rENG}Oh my God, I'm gonna take a picture of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:09.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,艾拉那个苹果吃完了吗\N{\rENG}Hey, did Ella finish that apple?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,你要从孩子嘴里抢食吃吗\N{\rENG}You're going to take food out of your child's mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:14.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 是的  - 好吧\N{\rENG}- Yeah.  - Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:17.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,都变成棕色了\N{\rENG}This all brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,没关系 还有一块可以吃\N{\rENG}No no, there is a spot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:28.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,艾拉 这是你爸爸偷你食物的证据\N{\rENG}Ella, this is evidence of your father stealing food from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:31.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,不管你变得贪食还是厌食\N{\rENG}If you become bulimic or anorexic,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:34.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,都不是我的错 别全怪你妈妈 好吗\N{\rENG}it's not my fault, don't blame it all on your mother, Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,艾拉 这是个家庭分享苹果\N{\rENG}Ella, this is a family apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:38.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,我在教她们分享的重要性\N{\rENG}I'm teaching them the value of sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:39.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,宝贝我爱你\N{\rENG}I love you, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:43.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,多甜蜜啊 姑娘们会比咱们还要深刻地\N{\rENG}Ahhh, so sweet, you girls will remember this vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:44.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,铭记着这次与众不同的假期\N{\rENG}very different than we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:45.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,那是肯定的\N{\rENG}That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:46.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,从我妈那里我就知道了\N{\rENG}I see that with my mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,她对我童年的印象和我完全不同\N{\rENG}she remembers my childhood entirely different than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,别拍我了\N{\rENG}Please stop filming me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:56.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,天啊 我爱你妈妈 你对她太苛刻了\N{\rENG}God. I love your mom, you're always so hard on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:58.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,因为你错过了那些操蛋的岁月\N{\rENG}It is because you missed the fucked-up years,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:09:59.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,你赶上了好时候\N{\rENG}you are just getting the good era.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,操蛋的岁月\N{\rENG}The fucked-up years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:03.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,说到操蛋我想起来了\N{\rENG}That reminds me, talking about fucked-up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:06.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你我那只艳后猫咪的事吗\N{\rENG}did I ever tell you the story about my little Cleopatra kitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:11.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,我记不得了 我要是说过你肯定有印象\N{\rENG}I dunno? Ok. I think you would remember if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,故事是这样的\N{\rENG}It's the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:15.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,我小时候养了只猫 起名叫埃及艳后\N{\rENG}You know when I was a little girl I had this cat named Cleopatra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:18.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,每到春天她都会跳出栅栏然后怀孕\N{\rENG}And every spring she would jump the fence and get pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:23.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,每次都会生出恰好两只猫咪\N{\rENG}And always end up with a litter of exactly two kittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:27.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 恰好两只  - 每次 每年都是两只\N{\rENG}- Two kitties.  - Every time, every year, two cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:30.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,很神奇 在我三十岁左右的某一天\N{\rENG}I mean... it's just amazing, then one days I was like around 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:34.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,我和我爸爸一起吃午饭 回忆过去\N{\rENG}And I was having lunch with my dad and was remembering,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:36.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,提到了小埃及艳后\N{\rENG}mentioning little Cleopatra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:39.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,他说自己做过最艰难的事\N{\rENG}And he was like... the hardest thing I ever had to do
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:42.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是杀掉那些可爱的小猫咪\N{\rENG}was to kill those cute little kittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:43.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我惊讶极了\N{\rENG}And I was like what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:46.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,我告诉你 其实就是这么回事\N{\rENG}It turns out ... listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:50.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,有时她会一窝生出七只猫咪\N{\rENG}There was sometimes up to 7 kittens in that litter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:52.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,我爸爸就拿走五只\N{\rENG}But he would take 5 of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,把它们放进一个塑料袋 然后灌乙醚\N{\rENG}put them in a plastic bag, with a bunch of ether.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:57.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,太可怕了\N{\rENG}That is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:11:00.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,就好像 他似乎忘记了\N{\rENG}That was like... He had forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:03.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,当初他和妈妈是怎么骗我的了\N{\rENG}the lie he and my mum had told me about the kittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:04.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,他怎么决定该杀哪几只呢\N{\rENG}How did he decide which ones he wanted to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:05.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,其实我倒真问过他\N{\rENG}Well actually I asked him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:09.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,是不是拿走最毛茸茸的 最可爱的\N{\rENG}Did you take the, you know, the fluffiest, cutest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:13.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后他就开始哭 可怜的老爸\N{\rENG}You know, and he just started to cry, poor daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:16.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,咱们说过要在这里停车的\N{\rENG}Oh we said we would gonna stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,孩子们要看遗迹\N{\rENG}They wanted to see the ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:20.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 没错  - 艾拉特想看\N{\rENG}- Yeah.  - Well, Ella really wanted to ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:22.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 但是咱们该把她们叫醒吗\N{\rENG}Yes, but should we wake them up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:27.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,咱们回机场的路上可以叫她们看\N{\rENG}You know, on the way back to the airport, we can catch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 咱们不会的  - 没错 大概是\N{\rENG}- You know we won't.  - Yeah, probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:33.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,再见了古代遗迹 不过你有什么好看的\N{\rENG}So long ancient ruins! What is so great about you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:35.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,窥一斑可见全豹\N{\rENG}You seen one, you seen them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:39.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,天啊 咱们真是对糟糕的父母\N{\rENG}Oh my God, we are shitty parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,咱们应该停车的\N{\rENG}We should have stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 没事的  - 这是文化 掉头吧\N{\rENG}- It's Ok.  - It's culture, come on, go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:45.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,咱们得培养她们一些品质\N{\rENG}We gotta put some character to these kids somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,咱们在教她们重要的一课\N{\rENG}I mean, we are teaching them a valuable lesson.
