Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.04,0:53:05.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道 这可不是个好问题\N{\rENG}You know that is not even a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.90,0:53:10.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,真正的问题是如果我邀请你和我一起下车\N{\rENG}The real question would be if I did ask you to get off the train.
