Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.44,0:57:08.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你会活得比我长的  - 到时候就知道了\N{\rENG}- You're gonna outlive me.  - We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.74,0:57:10.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想我们俩只有一个人能看到那一天\N{\rENG}I guess one of us will see.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.96,0:57:14.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,你觉得我们也葬在一起怎么样\N{\rENG}What do you think you're gonna go to the service with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.81,0:57:18.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 去德克萨斯吗  - 反正不在巴黎\N{\rENG}- To Texas?  - It's not gonna be in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.14,0:57:20.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,你有多想把我葬在那儿\N{\rENG}Ok, how bad you want me there?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.32,0:57:23.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,其实我很愿意去 只不过机票太贵了\N{\rENG}I mean I would come but it's really expensive with the flights.
