Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.82,0:57:41.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 你还能再忍受我五十六年吗\N{\rENG}Well... will you be able to put up with me for 56 more years?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.01,0:57:45.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我也想知道  - 你又来了\N{\rENG}- I'm looking forward to it.  - Shit, you're really working it.
