Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.40,1:01:13.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我才不上当呢  - 说什么呢\N{\rENG}- I am not answering that.  - What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.35,1:01:16.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,难道我身上就没有一点是你想改变的吗\N{\rENG}There is not one thing that you would like to change about me?
