Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.13,1:01:19.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 好吧 其实  - 就说一个\N{\rENG}- Ok, actually,  - One thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.56,1:01:21.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你能改变一个地方\N{\rENG}if I could change one thing about you,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.86,1:01:25.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,我希望你不要再试图改变我了\N{\rENG}it would be for you to stop trying to change me.
