Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.32,1:08:11.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是明天在你身边醒来\N{\rENG}Is waking up next to you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.97,1:08:14.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是说 没有妮娜和艾拉在边上蹦蹦跳跳\N{\rENG}You mean, without Nina and Ella jumping on our heads?
