Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.28,1:39:17.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rENG}Ok...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.33,1:39:20.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,我把这个年轻人派去你身边\N{\rENG}I'm sending you this young man,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.41,1:39:22.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 年轻人\N{\rENG}yes, young.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.20,1:39:24.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,他会是你的护卫\N{\rENG}And he will be your escort.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.02,1:39:27.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,天晓得他有多少毛病\N{\rENG}God knows he has many problems
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.30,1:39:30.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,他终其一生都在\N{\rENG}and he's struggled his whole life connecting
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.69,1:39:35.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,努力亲近陪伴他最爱的人\N{\rENG}and being present, even with those he loves the most.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.35,1:39:37.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,对此 他万分抱歉\N{\rENG}And, for that, he is deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.36,1:39:41.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是你是他唯一的希望\N{\rENG}But you are his only hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.90,1:39:43.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,瑟琳\N{\rENG}Celine,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.40,1:39:46.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,我对你的建议是\N{\rENG}my advice to you is this:
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.49,1:39:49.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,你已经进入人生中最美好的年华\N{\rENG}You're entering the best years of your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.16,1:39:52.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,从我这个年纪回望过去\N{\rENG}Looking back from where I sit now,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.99,1:39:57.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,这段中年岁月仅比你十二岁和马修·瓦内萨\N{\rENG}these middle years are only a little bit more difficult
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.43,1:40:02.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,彻夜欢跳比吉斯的“你的爱有多深”\N{\rENG}than when you were 12 and Matthew and Vanessa
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.16,1:40:06.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,要艰难一些\N{\rENG}danced all night to the Bee Gees' "How deep is your love".
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.37,1:40:07.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不知道是什么\N{\rENG}I don't know what that...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.64,1:40:10.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,算了 瑟琳 你会没事的\N{\rENG}Anyway... Celine, you will be fine,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.96,1:40:13.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的女儿们会成长为\N{\rENG}your girls will grow up to become examples
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.46,1:40:16.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 女权运动的典范  - 不错\N{\rENG}- and icons of feminism.  - Nice one.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.49,1:40:18.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 我刚注意到\N{\rENG}Yeah. Well you know I just noticed that
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.15,1:40:21.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,底下有一段附言\N{\rENG}there's a postscript on the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.13,1:40:23.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许我应该跳过 这些太无聊了\N{\rENG}Maybe I just skip over, some of this is kind of boring...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.27,1:40:24.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 跳过 跳过\N{\rENG}Yes. Skip away, please, skip away.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.69,1:40:26.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你确定  - 是\N{\rENG}- Ok... you sure?  - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.08,1:40:28.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 好的  - 絮絮叨叨的\N{\rENG}- Alright, well...  - Boring stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.81,1:40:31.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 下面就是说什么\N{\rENG}Ok... yeah, it's like blah blah blah,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.64,1:40:35.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,经济注意事项啦 星座啦\N{\rENG}financial tips, horoscopes...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.06,1:40:39.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,好了这里 附言 顺便说下\N{\rENG}Ok... Here it is: P.S. By the way...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.11,1:40:47.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,顺便说下 我一生中最棒的性体验\N{\rENG}By the way, the best sex of my life happened one night
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.36,1:40:49.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,是在伯罗奔尼撒南部的一夜\N{\rENG}in the Southern Peloponnese.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.29,1:40:51.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,别错过\N{\rENG}Don't miss it!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.45,1:40:57.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的性福达到一个新的里程碑\N{\rENG}My whole sexual being went to a whole new ground-breaking level.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.37,1:40:59.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,新的里程碑 很好\N{\rENG}Ground-breaking, great.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.70,1:41:01.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 你知道这什么意思吗\N{\rENG}Yeah ... you know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.22,1:41:03.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,杰西 能停止这个愚蠢的游戏吗\N{\rENG}Ok. Jesse. Can you stop this stupid game?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.48,1:41:06.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们不是你小说里的人物\N{\rENG}We're not in one of your stories.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.49,1:41:07.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\rENG}Ok?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.43,1:41:10.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,你听到我返回房间说的话吗\N{\rENG}Did you hear what I said to you back in the room?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.83,1:41:11.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,你听到了吗\N{\rENG}Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.33,1:41:14.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.47,1:41:15.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,听到了\N{\rENG}I heard you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.11,1:41:19.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不爱我了吗\N{\rENG}What, that you don't love me anymore?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.39,1:41:22.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,我以为你不是那意思 但如果你就是那意思\N{\rENG}I figured you didn't mean it but if you did then...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.77,1:41:26.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\rENG}Oh, fuck it, you know something?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.93,1:41:28.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,你就像个小女孩\N{\rENG}You're just like the little girls
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.19,1:41:31.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,希望周围的人都生活在童话中\N{\rENG}and everybody else you want to live inside some fairy tale, alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.33,1:41:33.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,我来这是想挽回 好吗\N{\rENG}I'm just trying to make things better here, alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.75,1:41:35.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我告诉你我无条件爱你\N{\rENG}I tell you that I love you unconditionally,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.45,1:41:36.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我告诉你你很美\N{\rENG}I tell you that you're beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.59,1:41:39.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,我告诉你你的屁股八十岁都风采依旧\N{\rENG}I tell you that your ass looks great when you're 80
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.36,1:41:44.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我努力想逗你笑  - 好吧\N{\rENG}- I'm trying to make you laugh.  - Ok
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.92,1:41:47.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,我忍受你一大堆臭脾气\N{\rENG}I've put up with plenty of your shit
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.24,1:41:50.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你以为我是条狗 总是回来找你\N{\rENG}and if you think I'm just some dog who's gonna keep coming back,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.80,1:41:56.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,那你错了 但如果你想要真爱 这就是爱\N{\rENG}then you're wrong. But if you want true love then this is it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.71,1:41:59.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就是生活 不完美但很真实\N{\rENG}This is real life. It's not perfect but it's real,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.69,1:42:01.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你看不到 那是你瞎了\N{\rENG}and if you can not see it then you're blind.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.87,1:42:03.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吗 我放弃\N{\rENG}Alright? I give up.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.00,1:42:43.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,时光机是什么样的\N{\rENG}So what about this time machine?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.78,1:42:48.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\N{\rENG}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.83,1:42:51.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么工作的\N{\rENG}How does it work?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.50,1:42:54.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,很复杂\N{\rENG}Well, it's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.42,1:43:01.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,操作时要光着身子吗\N{\rENG}Am I gonna have to get naked to operate it?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.18,1:43:10.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我是说  - 是的 真是这样\N{\rENG}- I mean...  - Yeah, it's actually, it's been a real issue.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.30,1:43:11.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是说不穿…衣服\N{\rENG}I mean, I don't...clothes,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.00,1:43:14.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,不能顺利通过时空统一体\N{\rENG}they just don't travel well through whole space-time continuum.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.40,1:43:21.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,哇哦 你真聪明\N{\rENG}Wow, you're so smart.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.76,1:43:24.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,- Jesus  - 时空\N{\rENG}- Jesus.  - Space-time?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.35,1:43:28.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 统一体  - 统一体\N{\rENG}- Continuum.  - Continuum?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.30,1:43:29.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.02,1:43:34.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道我在想着你这封信\N{\rENG}You know something I've been thinking about your letter...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.38,1:43:39.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,你说你在伯罗奔尼撒南部住过\N{\rENG}You know you... you lived in the Southern Peloponnese?
