Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.56,1:43:47.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,你说今晚会不会就是你八十岁时\N{\rENG}And do you think it could be tonight
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.14,1:43:49.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,依旧念念不忘的夜晚\N{\rENG}that you are still talking about in your 80s?
